title: Ukrainian military had 67 combat engagements with Russian forces near Bilohorivka, Zolotarivka of Luhansk region and Yampoliv...
content: UKRANIAN MILITARY HAD 67 Combat Engagagements with Russian Forces Near Bilohorivka, Zolotarivka of Luhansk Region and Yampolivka, Terny, Vesele of Donetsk Region, Bohdani VKA, IVANIVSKE, KLISCHIIIVKA of DONETSK Region, Berdychi, Semenivka, Tonenke, Pervomayske, Netaylove, NEVELSKE of DONETSK Region, Krasnohorivka, Heorhiyivka, Novomykhaylivka, Vodyane, Uroozhayne, Staromayorske of Donetsk Region and Robotyne of Zaporizhia Region, At the Eastern Bank of Dni Pro River in Kherson Region - General Staff of Armed Forces of Ukraine Says in the Evening Report
